==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Christocentric
<hw>Chris"to*cen"tric</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Christ</ets> + <ets>centric</ets>.]</ety> <def>Making Christ
the center, about whom all things are grouped, as in religion or
history; tending toward Christ, as the central object of thought or
emotion.</def> <rj><au>J. W. Chadwick.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Christology</ent>⟦br⟧
